msgid "Redstone Link"
msgstr ""

#. type: Plain text
#: ../src/redstone-link.adoc:4
msgid ""
"Redstone links enable remote transmission and reception of redstone signals, "
"as described in their in-game ponder. When placed in factory controllers, "
"they may be connected with other components with redstone capabilities, "
"allowing them to interoperate with contraptions outside the factory "
"controller."
msgstr ""

